                                    <td align="center" background="/imagelib/sitebuilder/layout/spacer.gif"><img alt="Goldsboro North Carolina Map.jpg" border="" src="sitebuildercontent/sitebuilderpictures/battleofwhitehall.jpg" vspace="0" hspace="5"><br></td>
